one else there, but Id rather have self respect and honor, and know that guild might possibly return the favor some day, than to be known as a total dickhead with good gear. </P><P>I think Guild A should have been allowed to mess with Gore. If they couldnt take her, theyd give up. If they killed her eventually, good for them.</P><P><img src="http://www.netset.com/~blazer/demotivator2.jpg" border=0></P><P></font></td>
